<%- include('/partials/head') %>

<span class="eyebrow">Library System · Welcome</span>
<h1>Your next great read is already on the shelf.</h1>
<p style="max-width:44ch; font-size:1.05rem;">
  Browse the catalog, reserve a title in seconds, and get notified the moment
  it's ready — no more walking to the library just to find it's checked out.
</p>

<div style="display:flex; gap:0.8rem; margin-top:1.5rem;">
  <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/auth/signup">Sign up — it's free</a>
  <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/auth/login">Log in</a>
</div>

<hr class="perforation">

<div class="page-header">
  <div>
    <span class="eyebrow">Why students use it</span>
    <h2 style="margin:0;">Everything, without the guesswork</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="stack-grid">
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="tag">Browse</span>
    <h3>Search the whole catalog</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">Every title in one place — no more wondering what's actually on the shelf.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="tag alt">Reserve</span>
    <h3>Hold a book in seconds</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">One click reserves it for you — staff approve it, and it's yours to collect.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="tag">Track</span>
    <h3>Always know your status</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">Pending, confirmed, or expired — your dashboard shows exactly where you stand.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="tag alt">14 days</span>
    <h3>No rush, no penalty stress</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">Every reservation holds for two full weeks once approved — plenty of time to swing by.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="perforation">

<div class="page-header">
  <div>
    <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
    <h2 style="margin:0;">Three steps, that's it</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="stack-grid">
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="stamp available">Step 1</span>
    <h3>Create an account</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">Takes under a minute — just a username, email, and password.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="stamp available">Step 2</span>
    <h3>Find and reserve a book</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">Search the catalog and reserve whatever catches your eye.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="book-card">
    <span class="stamp available">Step 3</span>
    <h3>Collect it from the library</h3>
    <p class="author" style="margin:0;">Once staff approve your hold, it's waiting for you at the counter.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="perforation">

<div style="text-align:center; padding: 1rem 0 2rem;">
  <h2 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Ready to reserve your first book?</h2>
  <p style="margin:0 0 1.2rem;">It only takes a minute to get started.</p>
  <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/auth/signup">Create your account</a>
</div>

<%- include('/partials/footer') %>
